title: Person of Interest - 4x11 - Reese saves Finch
author: YT.POI
comment: John will do anything for his lovers.
Thank you so much for uploading this scene!

Why on earth do I love Lambert so much
I love Reese too but Lambert seems to be my fav

I'm pretty sure Reese would have gone to press the override button, alone or with Shaw I don't know. So if you love him as I do, you should thank Lambert. Fusco and Finch would've also done the same thing but one of them doesn't use weapons and the other one has a son.
